  "slug": "wildlife-fabric",
  "title": "Wildlife [Fabric]",
  "description": "Adds extra animals and insects to Minecraft!",
  "body": "<p><img alt=\"Wildlife Banner Image\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VY8MNuM.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"686\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Important:</strong> This mod requires Geckolib for Fabric. Patchouli is optional, but necessary for the guidebook.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Supported Mod Loaders:</strong> Fabric</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #ff9900;\"><br /></span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Mod Highlights:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Adds 74 different kinds of animals and insects to the world.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Insects and smaller animals can be caught/released by right-clicking them.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Each species of songbird has its own unique birdsong.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Small animals can be placed on top of players' heads and on itemframes.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Rare albino variants.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Includes a Patchouli book with descriptions/illustrations for each animal.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Includes a config file that can be used to adjust spawn locations/frequency.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>&nbsp;Small animals can be caught by right-clicking on them with an empty hand and will ride on a player's head if placed there ^_^</em><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"A series of screenshots showing how to pick up a chickadee\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tJktzRs.png\" width=\"1125\" height=\"387\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Birds</strong></span></p>\n<table style=\"height: 439px;\" width=\"842\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Bluebirds</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Black-Capped Chickadees</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Cottonbirds</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Scarlet Flycatchers</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Goldfinchs</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lark Buntings</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Meadowlarks</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Orioles</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Phoebes</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Robins</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Sparrows</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Swallows</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Towhee</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">White-eyed Vireos</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Wrens&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Birds\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/coi8t63.png\" width=\"396\" height=\"396\" /></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Mammals</strong></span><strong><br />_______________________________________________________________________________ <br /><br /></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rek1GIg.png\" alt=\"Mammals\" width=\"870\" height=\"450\" /></span></p>\n<table style=\"height: 144px;\" width=\"421\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Anteaters</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Armadillos</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Badgers</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Beavers</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Boars<br /><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"25\" /></span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Capybaras</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Deer</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ferrets</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Hamsters</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"25\" /><br /></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Hedgehogs</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Monkeys</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Porcupines</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Possums</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\"  width=\"200\" height=\"25\" /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br /></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Reptiles</strong></span><strong><br />_______________________________________________________________________________ <br /><br /></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Reptiles\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kTYBQBj.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"346\" /></span></p>\n<table style=\"height: 110px;\" width=\"477\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Chameleons<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Geckos</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Grass Snakes</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Iguanas<br /></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\"  src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">King Snakes<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Milk Snakes</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Pythons<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Alligators<br /></span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Fish &amp; Aquatic Creatures</strong><strong><br />_______________________________________________________________________________ <br /><br /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Fish and Aquatic Creatures\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6ycGdtw.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"498\" /></span></p>\n<table style=\"height: 177px;\" width=\"950\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Goldfish</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Betta fish</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Bluegill</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Catfish<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Koi</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Shrimp</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Seahorse<br /></span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Seahorse</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Jellyfish<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Freshwater Prawns</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Glow Jellyfish</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Sea Urchins</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Clams</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Horseshoe Crabs<br /></span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Starfish</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Sand Dollars</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Stingrays</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Manta Rays<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Anglerfish</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Hammerhead Sharks</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Rainbow Trout<br /></span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Insects &amp; Arthropods</strong><strong><br />_______________________________________________________________________________ <br /><br /></strong><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d9QF0ld.png\" alt=\"Insects and Arthropods\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<table style=\"height: 177px;\" width=\"950\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ants</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Crickets</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Dragonflies</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Glasswing Butterflies<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">June Beetles</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ladybugs<br /></span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Monarch Butterflies</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Blue Morpho Butterflies<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Rhino Beetles</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Snails</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Spicebush Butterflies</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Spiders<br /></span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img alt=\"Spacer image\" alt=\"spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Staghorn Beetles</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Stickbugs</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Sunflower Beetles</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Tiger Swallowtail Butterflies<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Crabs</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Hermit crabs<br /></span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img  alt=\"spacer image\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lYvYORa.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"25\" /></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><em><strong>Compatible with Patchouli:<br /></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Use a book on a wildlife mob to get the guidebook.</span></em> <br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><em><strong>_______________________________________________________________________________ <br /></strong></em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"A screenshot of the Patchouli guidebook.\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HLZOQjY.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1108\" height=\"586\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><em><strong>Itemframes:</strong></em><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><em><strong>_______________________________________________________________________________ <br /><br /></strong></em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"A screenshot of the itemframes\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rn3xnT4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"738\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img alt=\"Thank you banner\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/866521661880795147/880298426808565770/andspecialthanks21.png\" alt=\"Acknowledgements and special thanks\" width=\"320\" height=\"64\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Many thanks to the project's patrons: <strong>Zura, Lavie, Kree, Atlan, Le fl&eacute;mmard, Eugene Nubberslaw, Azilea_Royalty, and Nil!</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Please consider supporting the developers on <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/chirpycricket\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Patreon</a> if you like the mods!</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
